OL,3,CSouthampton family preparing to move
OL,4,Cthousands of miles to isolated island
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's Harry Acton
OL,7,Fspoke to the Wall's family at their
OL,8,Fhome in Southampton.
OL,10,FA family from Southampton are
OL,11,Fpreparing to move thousands of miles
OL,12,Facross the globe to dedicate their
OL,13,Flives to helping some of the most
OL,14,Fisolated people on the planet.
OL,16,FRichard and Christine, are taking
OL,17,Ftheir two children Eloise and Rupert,
OL,18,Fto Papua New Guinea (PNG).
