OL,3,CSouthampton family preparing to move
OL,4,Cthousands of miles to isolated island
OL,6,FThe family hope it will give them a
OL,7,Fnew purpose in life, and will be
OL,8,Fworking with the charity, Mission
OL,9,FAviation Fellowship (MAF), to make a
OL,10,Fdifference to communities in the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FRichard, who is a qualified pilot,
OL,14,Fwill take up a new role flying small
OL,15,Fsupply planes in the region, which are
OL,16,Fcritical in navigating the more than
OL,17,F600 islands that make up PNG.
