OL,3,CSouthampton family preparing to move
OL,4,Cthousands of miles to isolated island
OL,6,FChristine, who used to work for
OL,7,FBritish Airways as cabin crew, will at
OL,8,Ffirst take up a role homeschooling the
OL,9,Fchildren, as there is no education in
OL,10,Fthe country.
OL,12,FBoth say they are ready to face the
OL,13,Fchallenges, but acknowledge it won't
OL,14,Fbe easy.
OL,16,F"We've had a really comfortable life
OL,17,Fhere", Christine told ITV Meridian.
OL,18,F"It has been really comfortable, and
OL,19,Fwe have been doing 9 to 5 and
OL,20,Feverything, but we just really feel
OL,21,Four skills can be used over there.
