OL,6,F"I am lucky enough that I have my
OL,7,Fpilot's license". Richard said. "It
OL,8,Fwasn't cheap to get in the first
OL,9,Fplace, but we can use those skills to
OL,10,Fbe able to help and work alongside
OL,11,Fcommunities that otherwise wouldn't
OL,12,Fhave that help and support."
OL,14,FThe Wall's family say they're excited
OL,15,Fto move thousands of miles away.
OL,17,FThe couple say they're hopeful that
OL,18,Fthe children will adjust to their new
OL,19,Fenvironment. They sought expert advice
OL,20,Fbefore deciding to make the move.
