OL,6,FAs they are both young, the family
OL,7,Fhave been told they should thrive in
OL,8,Ftheir new environments.
OL,10,FIf they have any problems they will be
OL,11,Fsupported by MAF, who have already
OL,12,Fhelped families relocate to the region
OL,13,Ffrom the UK.
OL,15,FThe charity has been active for 75
OL,16,Fyears, and relies on families like the
OL,17,FWall's, to help them with their
OL,18,Fmission.
