OL,4,Cthousands of miles to isolated island
OL,6,FPapua New Guinea has some of the most
OL,7,Ftreacherous terrain in the world, and
OL,8,Fthe light aircraft funded by MAF play
OL,9,Fa key role in keeping the islands
OL,10,Fconnected.
OL,12,FThe charity has also introduced solar
OL,13,Fpower and some limited technology to
OL,14,Fthe islands, to bring the diverse
OL,15,Fcommunities closer together.
OL,17,FThe Wall's will be out in PNG for
OL,18,Faround 4 years, but will be able to
OL,19,Fstay for longer if they choose too.
