OL,6,FThey know it will be tough, but hope
OL,7,Fthat they and the children will thrive.
OL,9,FVivienne Pattison, said: "The Wall
OL,10,Ffamily are really needed because in
OL,11,FPapua New Guinea, where they're going,
OL,12,F86% of people live in rural areas. And
OL,13,Fof that 86%, about three-quarters of
OL,14,Fthem don't have adequate
OL,15,Ftransportation.
