OL,6,F"Now to us, we think that's a bus or a
OL,7,Ftrain but actually it could be the
OL,8,Fdifference between getting to the
OL,9,Fhospital, getting vaccinations,
OL,10,Fgetting an education, getting food or
OL,11,Fthe essentials of life.
OL,13,F"So actually what the Walls are going
OL,14,Fto be doing will make a huge
OL,15,Fdifference to the community in Papua
OL,16,FNew Guinea."
